  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 at Model Risk Level 3 following a regulatory query regarding device classification uplift. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet or exceed required levels. The 'Use error' factor is documented as not assessed on the grounds that operator interaction with the simulation software is considered outside the scope of this COU; however, the package does not formally encode this exclusion as 'not-applicable', leaving a material credibility gap at MRL 3.",
