      "rationale": "Three independent test runs performed at each of five operating points using fresh bovine blood from separate draws. Hematocrit measured pre- and post-test (33±2%). Baseline plasma-free hemoglobin < 5 mg/dL confirmed for all samples. Inter-run variability in RH < 8%. Required level met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
