      "rationale": "Geometric model constructed from CMM scan of physical test pump; maximum surface deviation 0.03 mm. Flow rates and rotational speeds in simulation match experimental setpoints within 0.5% and 0.2% respectively. Fluid property equivalence documented via rheometry comparison. Input parameter equivalency confirmed across all five operating points. Required level met."
