    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 3. The 'Use error' factor was not assessed on the basis that simulation operator interaction was considered outside the scope of this context of use. The assessment team concluded that the remaining assessed factors provide sufficient evidence to support the credibility claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. All validation comparisons satisfy the pre-defined acceptance criterion (RH < 1; percent difference < 15%). The package is accepted for submission.",
